recipesList.title: Mango Salsa Chicken
recipesList.directions: Season chicken with salt and pepper. Grill until cooked. Dice mango, red onion, and cilantro. Mix diced ingredients with lime juice. Serve grilled chicken topped with mango salsa.
recipesList.author: Guru

recipesList.title: Vegetarian Pasta Primavera
recipesList.directions: Boil pasta until al dente. Sauté vegetables in olive oil and garlic. Toss cooked pasta with sautéed vegetables. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese before serving.
recipesList.author: Guru

recipesList.title: Spicy Shrimp Tacos
recipesList.directions: Season shrimp with spices and grill. Assemble tacos with grilled shrimp, shredded cabbage, sliced avocado, lime, and cilantro. Top with sour cream and hot sauce.
recipesList.author: Guru

recipesList.title: Classic Chocolate Chip Cookies
recipesList.directions: Cream butter and sugars. Add eggs and vanilla. Mix in dry ingredients. Fold in chocolate chips. Drop dough onto baking sheets. Bake until golden brown.
recipesList.author: Guru

recipesList.title: Caprese Salad
recipesList.directions: Slice tomatoes and mozzarella. Arrange on a plate with fresh basil leaves. Drizzle with balsamic glaze and olive oil. Season with salt and pepper.
recipesList.author: Guru
